 Cailee Spaeny 表示泰勒·斯威夫特是《Mare Of Easttown》的超级粉丝https://www.nme.com/news/film/cailee-spaeny-says-taylor-swift-is-a-huge-fan-of-mare-of-easttown-3616103?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=cailee-斯佩尼说泰勒·斯威夫特是东镇母马的超级粉丝Elizabeth AubreyWed, 10 Apr 2024 22:01:11 +0000 Film NewsMusic NewsTV NewsPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3616103 <p><img width="2000" height="1269" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Cailee-Spaeny-and-Taylor-SwiftPhoto-by-Rich-Polk_Golden-Globes-2024_Golden-Globes-2024-via-Getty-Images.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="凯莉·斯派尼和泰勒·斯威夫特" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Cailee-Spaeny-and-Taylor-SwiftPhoto-by-Rich-Polk_Golden-Globes-2024_Golden-Globes-2024-via-Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Cailee-Spaeny-and-Taylor-SwiftPhoto-by-Rich-Polk_Golden-Globes-2024_Golden-Globes-2024-via-Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Cailee-Spaeny-and-Taylor-SwiftPhoto-by-Rich-Polk_Golden-Globes-2024_Golden-Globes-2024-via-Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Cailee-Spaeny-and-Taylor-SwiftPhoto-by-Rich-Polk_Golden-Globes-2024_Golden-Globes-2024-via-Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Cailee-Spaeny-and-Taylor-SwiftPhoto-by-Rich-Polk_Golden-Globes-2024_Golden-Globes-2024-via-Getty-Images-1392x883.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Cailee-Spaeny-and-Taylor-SwiftPhoto-by-Rich-Polk_Golden-Globes-2024_Golden-Globes-2024-via-Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “泰勒·斯威夫特说她喜欢东镇的母马，这太疯狂了”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/cailee-spaeny-says-taylor-swift-is-a-huge-fan-of-mare-of-easttown-3616103">Cailee Spaeny 称泰勒·斯威夫特是《Mare Of Easttown》的超级粉丝的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1269" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Cailee-Spaeny-and-Taylor-SwiftPhoto-by-Rich-Polk_Golden-Globes-2024_Golden-Globes-2024-via-Getty-Images.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="凯莉·斯派尼和泰勒·斯威夫特" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Cailee-Spaeny-and-Taylor-SwiftPhoto-by-Rich-Polk_Golden-Globes-2024_Golden-Globes-2024-via-Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Cailee-Spaeny-and-Taylor-SwiftPhoto-by-Rich-Polk_Golden-Globes-2024_Golden-Globes-2024-via-Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Cailee-Spaeny-and-Taylor-SwiftPhoto-by-Rich-Polk_Golden-Globes-2024_Golden-Globes-2024-via-Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Cailee-Spaeny-and-Taylor-SwiftPhoto-by-Rich-Polk_Golden-Globes-2024_Golden-Globes-2024-via-Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Cailee-Spaeny-and-Taylor-SwiftPhoto-by-Rich-Polk_Golden-Globes-2024_Golden-Globes-2024-via-Getty-Images-1392x883.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Cailee-Spaeny-and-Taylor-SwiftPhoto-by-Rich-Polk_Golden-Globes-2024_Golden-Globes-2024-via-Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>卡莉·斯佩尼 (Cailee Spaeny) 回忆起她最近遇见<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/taylor-swift">泰勒·斯威夫特 (Taylor Swift) 的</a>那一刻，并公开了他们是如何通过<em>东镇母马 (Mare Of Easttown) 建立联系的。</em></p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/tv-reviews/mare-of-easttown-review-kate-winslet-2923609">《东镇的母马》评论：凯特·温斯莱特勇敢地面对小镇谋杀案的悲痛故事</a></strong></li></ul><p>这位演员曾在索菲亚·科波拉的<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/priscilla-review-elvis-presley-sofia-coppola-3493033">《普里西拉》</a></em>中饰演普里西拉·普雷西，接下来将在亚历克斯·<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/hbo">加兰</a>的<em>《内战》</em>中出演银幕。凯特·温斯莱特，<em>东镇的母马。</em></p><p>该剧于 2021 年首播，讲述了一位小镇侦探（凯特·温斯莱特饰演的马雷）调查青少年艾琳·麦克梅纳明谋杀案的故事。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/kate-winslet-celebrates-middle-aged-imperfect-mare-of-easttown-character-emmys-2021-3049601">温丝莱特随后凭借表演赢得 2021 年艾美奖限定剧、选集系列或电影女主角奖</a>。</p><p> “泰勒·斯威夫特说她很喜欢<em style="font-family: Verdana, BlinkMacSystemFont, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;">《东镇的马雷</em>》，这太疯狂了，鲁比说，‘我也喜欢<em style="font-family: Verdana, BlinkMacSystemFont, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;">《东镇的马雷</em>》！’”斯佩尼回忆道，她在接受<em><a href="https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/movies/movie-features/cailee-spaeny-talks-civil-war-taylor-swift-1235870573/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">《好莱坞报道》采访</a></em>时说道。</p><p>她继续说道：“然后泰勒说，‘但你在<em style="font-family: Verdana, BlinkMacSystemFont, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;">《伊斯特敦的马雷》</em>中是金发女郎，不是吗？’所以我不知道泰勒说了什么。也许只是因为她是<em style="font-family: Verdana, BlinkMacSystemFont, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;">东镇母马的</em>忠实粉丝，这非常酷。” </p><figure id="attachment_3020166" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3020166" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3020166" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/mare-of-easttown-season-one.jpg" alt="东镇母马" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/mare-of-easttown-season-one.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/mare-of-easttown-season-one-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/mare-of-easttown-season-one-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/mare-of-easttown-season-one-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/mare-of-easttown-season-one-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/mare-of-easttown-season-one-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3020166" class="wp-caption-text">凯特·温斯莱特和埃文·彼得斯在《东镇之海》中 图片来源：Sarah Shatz / HBO / 好莱坞档案馆</figcaption></figure><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/taylor-swift-1989-taylors-version-review-lyrics-tracklist-3522001">泰勒·斯威夫特 - “1989（泰勒版）”评论：她最好的专辑永远不会过时</a></strong></li></ul><p>温斯莱特此前曾<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/mare-of-easttown-season-2-kate-winslet-creator-some-very-cool-ideas-3012184">谈到<em>《伊斯特镇的母马》</em>回归第二季的可能性</a>，并表示该剧的创作者布拉德·英格尔斯比对下一步的发展有“一些非常酷的想法”。 “布拉德创造性地分享了一些非常酷的想法。我们会看看会发生什么，”她说。</p><p> “我还必须弄清楚我是否能做到。我可以再经历一遍吗？成为她确实让我在情感上付出了很大的代价，我必须弄清楚我是否可以再次振作起来并再次做到这一点。”</p><p> 《东镇的母马》被<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/nme-best-tv-shows-of-the-year-2021-3113636"><em>NME</em>评为 2021 年十大电视节目</a>之一，并获得<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/tv-reviews/mare-of-easttown-review-kate-winslet-2923609">四星评价</a>：“在经历了多年的悲剧之后，脾气暴躁、乐观向上、饱受打击的希恩是温斯莱特笔下迄今为止最阴郁的角色之一。她也是她最优秀的人之一。随着剧情慢慢展开（她也面临失去小孙子的监护权），马雷吸着电子烟，她拥有一种在男性主导的工作中生存所需的特殊韧性，她的每一个决定都受到严格审查。比男同事的还要多。</p><p> “来感受小镇的神秘，既扣人心弦又令人沮丧。留下真实银幕传奇人物的磁性表演，”我们的评论总结道。</p><p>与此同时，继 2022 年<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/grammys">格莱美</a>获奖作品<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/taylor-swift-midnights-review-3332805">《Midnights》</a>之后，斯威夫特将于下周五（4 月 19 日）发行她的第 11 张录音室唱片<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/taylor-swift-announces-new-album-the-tortured-poets-department-3582273">《The Tortured Poets Department》</a> 。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/cailee-spaeny-says-taylor-swift-is-a-huge-fan-of-mare-of-easttown-3616103">Cailee Spaeny 称泰勒·斯威夫特是《Mare Of Easttown》的超级粉丝的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
玛格特·罗比将制作“大片”新大富翁电影https://www.nme.com/news/film/margot-robbie-to- Produce-blockbuster-new-monopoly-movie-3616098?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=margot-robbie-to- Produce-blockbuster-new-垄断电影Elizabeth AubreyWed, 10 Apr 2024 21:28:58 +0000 Film NewsNews https://www.nme.com/?p=3616098 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Margot-Robbie-Photo-by-Leon-Bennett_GA_The-Hollywood-Reporter-via-Getty-Images.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="玛格特·罗比" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Margot-Robbie-Photo-by-Leon-Bennett_GA_The-Hollywood-Reporter-via-Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Margot-Robbie-Photo-by-Leon-Bennett_GA_The-Hollywood-Reporter-via-Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Margot-Robbie-Photo-by-Leon-Bennett_GA_The-Hollywood-Reporter-via-Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Margot-Robbie-Photo-by-Leon-Bennett_GA_The-Hollywood-Reporter-via-Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Margot-Robbie-Photo-by-Leon-Bennett_GA_The-Hollywood-Reporter-via-Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Margot-Robbie-Photo-by-Leon-Bennett_GA_The-Hollywood-Reporter-via-Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “这款游戏在全球范围内引起了几代人的共鸣，我们很高兴能够将这款游戏变为现实”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/margot-robbie-to-produce-blockbuster-new-monopoly-movie-3616098">玛格特·罗比制作“大片”新大富翁电影</a>后，首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Margot-Robbie-Photo-by-Leon-Bennett_GA_The-Hollywood-Reporter-via-Getty-Images.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="玛格特·罗比" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Margot-Robbie-Photo-by-Leon-Bennett_GA_The-Hollywood-Reporter-via-Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Margot-Robbie-Photo-by-Leon-Bennett_GA_The-Hollywood-Reporter-via-Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Margot-Robbie-Photo-by-Leon-Bennett_GA_The-Hollywood-Reporter-via-Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Margot-Robbie-Photo-by-Leon-Bennett_GA_The-Hollywood-Reporter-via-Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Margot-Robbie-Photo-by-Leon-Bennett_GA_The-Hollywood-Reporter-via-Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Margot-Robbie-Photo-by-Leon-Bennett_GA_The-Hollywood-Reporter-via-Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>今天（4 月 10 日）宣布，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/margot-robbie">玛格特·罗比</a>将根据棋盘游戏《大富翁》制作一部“轰动一时”的真人故事片。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/barbie-review-margot-robbie-ryan-gosling-3470019">《芭比娃娃》评论：格蕾塔·葛韦格的成人玩具故事非常有趣</a></strong></li></ul><p>该项目于今天在拉斯维加斯举行的 CinemaCon 上宣布，演员的制作公司 LuckyChap 被证实将与玩具公司孩之宝 (Hasbro) 合作制作这部电影。狮门影业将开发这部电影。</p><p> 《大富翁》是世界上最受欢迎的棋盘游戏之一，自 1900 年代初问世以来，销量已超过 5 亿份。</p><p>虽然剧情细节尚未公布，但狮门影业集团董事长 Adam Fogelson 表示，LuckyChap 对电影的拍摄方向有“明确的观点”。</p><p> “对于这个深受人们喜爱的标志性品牌，我无法想象有比 LuckyChap 更好的制作团队了，”福格尔森说道。 “他们是杰出的制作人，他们以深思熟虑和谨慎的态度选择自己的项目，并以清晰的观点加入大富翁。我们非常高兴能够与整个 LuckyChap 团队合作，共同开发我们相信将成为他们下一个重磅产品的产品。” </p><figure id="attachment_3573219" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3573219" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3573219" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Margot-Robbie-Barbie.jpg" alt="《芭比娃娃》中的玛格特·罗比" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Margot-Robbie-Barbie.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Margot-Robbie-Barbie-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Margot-Robbie-Barbie-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Margot-Robbie-Barbie-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Margot-Robbie-Barbie-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Margot-Robbie-Barbie-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3573219" class="wp-caption-text"> 《芭比娃娃》中的玛格特·罗比。图片来源：© 2023 华纳兄弟娱乐公司。保留所有权利。</figcaption></figure><p>孩之宝娱乐公司电影主管 Zev Foreman 补充道：“作为世界上最具标志性的游戏之一，《大富翁》为讲述故事的机会提供了一个令人难以置信的平台。我们很高兴能够拥有 LuckyChap 和狮门影业的独特愿景，与我们一起将这一具有历史意义的流行文化搬上大银幕。”</p><p> LuckyChap 在一份声明中表示：“《大富翁》是顶级财产——双关语。” “像所有最好的 IP 一样，这款游戏在全球范围内引起了几代人的共鸣，我们非常高兴能够与狮门影业和孩之宝的优秀团队一起将这款游戏变成现实。”</p><p>凯文·哈特（Kevin Hart）和<em style="font-family: Verdana, BlinkMacSystemFont, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;">《一路顺风》导演蒂姆·斯托里</em>（Tim Story）曾尝试过拍摄一部有关大富翁的电影。 Hart 于 2023 年向<a style="font-family: Verdana, BlinkMacSystemFont, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;" href="https://www.slashfilm.com/1312317/monopoly-movie-kevin-hart-director-tim-story/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener"><em>SlashFilm</em></a>证实，该项目“仍在开发中”。 “找到合适的东西是一件很困难的事情，”斯托里当时说道（来自<em><a href="https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/films/news/margot-robbie-monopoly-film-hasbro-b2526655.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">《独立报</a>》）。</em></p><p>罗比的制作公司还制作了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/barbie-beats-harry-potter-break-new-box-office-record-3490165#">2023 年票房最高的电影</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/films/barbie"><em>《芭比娃娃》</em></a> 。</p><p>这部由罗比主演的电影讲述了美泰标志性玩偶的故事，去年打破了票房纪录，全球票房收入达 14 亿美元（11.2 亿英镑）。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/margot-robbie-to-produce-blockbuster-new-monopoly-movie-3616098">玛格特·罗比制作“大片”新大富翁电影</a>后，首先在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上出现。</p> ;
 《罗密欧与朱丽叶》女演员弗兰西斯卡·阿梅乌达·里弗斯发表公开信，谴责“种族主义和厌恶女性的虐待” https://www.nme.com/news/tv/romeo-juliet-star-francesca-amewudah-rivers-backed-in-open-letter-condemning-racist-and-misogynistic-abuse-3616075?utm_source=rss&utm_medium= rss&utm_campaign=罗密欧-朱丽叶-明星-弗朗西斯卡-阿梅乌达-里弗斯支持公开信谴责种族主义和厌女症虐待Elizabeth AubreyWed, 10 Apr 2024 21:01:53 +0000 Film NewsNewsTV News.. https://www.nme.com/?p=3616075 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Romeo-and-Juliet-actress-backed-Photo-by-Ian-West_PA-Images-via-Getty-Images.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="弗朗西斯卡·阿梅乌达" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Romeo-and-Juliet-actress-backed-Photo-by-Ian-West_PA-Images-via-Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Romeo-and-Juliet-actress-backed-Photo-by-Ian-West_PA-Images-via-Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Romeo-and-Juliet-actress-backed-Photo-by-Ian-West_PA-Images-via-Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Romeo-and-Juliet-actress-backed-Photo-by-Ian-West_PA-Images-via-Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Romeo-and-Juliet-actress-backed-Photo-by-Ian-West_PA-Images-via-Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Romeo-and-Juliet-actress-backed-Photo-by-Ian-West_PA-Images-via-Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “针对如此可爱的灵魂的种族主义和厌恶女性的虐待让人难以忍受”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/romeo-juliet-star-francesca-amewudah-rivers-backed-in-open-letter-condemning-racist-and-misogynistic-abuse-3616075">《罗密欧与朱丽叶》女演员弗兰西斯卡·阿梅乌达-里弗斯在公开信中发表了谴责“种族主义和厌女症虐待”的公开信，该信</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Romeo-and-Juliet-actress-backed-Photo-by-Ian-West_PA-Images-via-Getty-Images.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="弗朗西斯卡·阿梅乌达" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Romeo-and-Juliet-actress-backed-Photo-by-Ian-West_PA-Images-via-Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Romeo-and-Juliet-actress-backed-Photo-by-Ian-West_PA-Images-via-Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Romeo-and-Juliet-actress-backed-Photo-by-Ian-West_PA-Images-via-Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Romeo-and-Juliet-actress-backed-Photo-by-Ian-West_PA-Images-via-Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Romeo-and-Juliet-actress-backed-Photo-by-Ian-West_PA-Images-via-Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Romeo-and-Juliet-actress-backed-Photo-by-Ian-West_PA-Images-via-Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>女演员弗兰西斯卡·阿梅乌达-里弗斯在公开信中表示支持，谴责她自出演<em>《罗密欧与朱丽叶》</em>以来所受到的“种族主义和厌恶女性的虐待”。</p><p>在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/heres-whos-starring-opposite-tom-holland-in-romeo-juliet-3610850">宣布演员阵容</a>（其中还包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/tom-holland">汤姆·赫兰德）</a>之后，阿梅乌达-里弗斯遭到了网上的“猛烈攻击”。</p><p>作为回应，杰米·劳埃德公司发表声明，谴责“网上针对我们公司成员的一系列令人遗憾的种族虐待行为”。</p><p>他们继续说道：“这必须停止。我们正在与一群杰出的艺术家合作。我们坚持认为他们可以自由创作作品，而不会面临网络骚扰。”</p><p> “我们不会容忍任何虐待行为，并将予以举报。欺凌和骚扰在网上、在我们的行业或更广泛的社区中都没有立足之地，”该剧院公司写道。</p><p> “我们庆祝我们令人难以置信的合作者的非凡才华。<em>罗密欧与朱丽叶</em>社区将继续以慷慨和爱心排练，并专注于我们作品的创作。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C5YSb6bIOey/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100